import React from "react";
import {
  BlockContentDiscription,
  BlockContentFooter,
  BlockLOGOFooter,
  ConatainerContentFooter,
  ContainerFooter,
} from "./style";
import LOGO from "../Logo/index";

import { FaMailBulk } from "react-icons/fa";

function Index() {
  return (
    <>
      <ContainerFooter>
        <ConatainerContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            <BlockLOGOFooter>
              <LOGO />
            </BlockLOGOFooter>
            <BlockContentDiscription>
              ShopeTeam - ứng dụng mua sắm trực tuyến thú vị, tin cậy, an toàn
              và miễn phí!
            </BlockContentDiscription>
            <BlockContentDiscription white>
              <FaMailBulk style={{ paddingRight: "20px" }} /> shopteam@gmail.com
            </BlockContentDiscription>
            <BlockContentDiscription white>
              <FaMailBulk style={{ paddingRight: "20px" }} /> shopteam@gmail.com
            </BlockContentDiscription>
            <BlockContentDiscription white>
              <FaMailBulk style={{ paddingRight: "20px" }} /> shopteam@gmail.com
            </BlockContentDiscription>
          </BlockContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            Our Recent Posts Visit Thailand, Bali And China September 7, 2016
            The Sound Of Our Jungle September 7, 2016 Visit Thailand, Bali And
            China September 7, 2016
          </BlockContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            Subscribe to our Newsletter Etiam rhoncus. Maecenas temp us, tellus
            eget condimentum rho
          </BlockContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            Our Instagram Aliquam lorem ante, dapibus inviver raqui feugiat a,
            tellus. Phasellus null
          </BlockContentFooter>
        </ConatainerContentFooter>
      </ContainerFooter>
    </>
  );
}

export default Index;
